@META
dir: skillsPraut/src/components/code/
updated: 2026-04-09
files: 10
stack: React, Remotion, TypeScript

@EXPORTS
APIRequest.tsx: APIRequest — method + URL + request/response code blocks
CodeBlock.tsx: CodeBlock — syntax-highlighted code (naive regex highlighter)
CodeDiff.tsx: CodeDiff — diff view with add/remove/context line coloring
CodeTypewriter.tsx: CodeTypewriter — CodeBlock with character-by-character typing
CommandLine.tsx: CommandLine — single-line CLI prompt with typewriter + blinking cursor
CurlExample.tsx: CurlExample — curl command + response in TerminalWindow
EditorWindow.tsx: EditorWindow — VS Code-like editor with tabs + code area
FileTree.tsx: FileTree — file/folder tree with active file highlight
JSONViewer.tsx: JSONViewer — pretty-printed JSON with color-coded types
TerminalWindow.tsx: TerminalWindow — macOS terminal window with traffic-light dots

@INTERFACES
FileNode: { name: string, type: "file"|"folder", active?: boolean, children?: FileNode[] }
DiffLine: { type: "add"|"remove"|"context", text: string }

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: styles/tokens (colors, fonts, frame, withOpacity) | hooks/useTypewriter | icons/PhosphorIcon
external: remotion (interpolate, useCurrentFrame)

@STANDARDS
- CodeBlock uses naive regex highlighter — no external syntax lib
- Keywords highlighted in purple[600], strings in success, numbers in blue[400]
- All code windows use navy[950] background + blue[400] border at 25% opacity
- TerminalWindow title default: "praut@macbook ~ %"
- Method colors: GET=success, POST=blue, PUT=warning, DELETE=error, PATCH=purple
